data.description: Charming 4 bedroom home located in Southern Hills. This well maintained cape-cod has over 1,600 sq ft w/ a full basement. Mature landscaping & an attractive front covered patio. Enter into the cozy living room w/ gas fireplace. The dining room has a gorgeous ship lap wall & is flooded w/ natural light from the large window. Kitchen has been fully remodeled w/ gorgeous white cabinets, new counter tops & back splash & all stainless steel appliances. New flooring throughout. 2 bedrooms & a full bath complete the 1st level. Upstairs is an open area that can be used as office space, a reading loft or even a play area. Along w/ 2 additional bedrooms & extra storage cabinets/closets. The full basement has new flooring throughout, a spacious rec area, an office or potential 5th bedroom, a full bathroom, separate storage area and a fully laundry room. Wow!! House & garage are connected by a breezeway which is the perfect mudroom area. Wait until you see the backyard!! Sit back, relax and enjoy life on the deck that overlooks the spacious fenced in yard. This home has a 1 car garage but is also located on a corner which allows for even extra parking!
